{"tid":286244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【幼園大爆炸】22歲疑兇相曝光 當場炸死牆寫「死亡滅絕」","createTime":"2017-06-16T12:38:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T18:05:47.000Z","uid":39464,"like":58,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"664e8f0b50fa1e6da1db25cc8fbee7b29d53351b","tid":286244,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T12:38:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170616/large/1497606034_94d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170616%2Flarge%2F1497606034_94d4.jpg&h=8f789036&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 江蘇徐州豐縣幼兒園大爆炸案已告破，22歲的疑犯許某某當場被炸身亡。許某某因自律神經功能失調從學校休學後，在案發地附近租住打工。在其租住房內發現留有自製爆炸裝置材料，並在牆上多處留有「死」、「亡」、」滅」、「絕」等字跡。事件至今，已造成8人死亡，65人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n另據教育部網站消息，日前，教育部印發《關於加強中小學（幼兒園）周邊安全風險防控工作的緊急通知》，要求各地加強學校周邊安全風險防控工作，確保廣大師生生命安全。<br />\n<br />\n觀察者網／央視 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170616/56836208\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170616%2F56836208&d=y8vGd2OV3ghg%2BXms0zhxk57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=e5f4de0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170616%2F56836208&h=0dddc791\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170616/56836208</a>"},{"pid":"f7e8a40e4a0979102bd4284b48abf900e0aa6318","tid":286244,"uid":10692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T13:01:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"40d8d9e166fb1fecc4593dc6863533a5f6561e92","tid":286244,"uid":58099,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T13:03:41.000Z","msg":"周杰倫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"691c492caec1e5a039747603280e1750d34f9670","tid":286244,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T13:04:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eser